      <title>两名俄罗斯国民是在阿富汗上空失踪的飞机上的乘客 - 塔斯社</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/two-russian-nationals-were-passengers-jet-which-went-missing-over-afghanistan-2024-01-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯国营塔斯社周日援引“运营部门”消息人士的话称，两名俄罗斯公民是一架飞往莫斯科的包机乘客，该包机在阿富汗上空失踪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/two-russian-nationals-were-passengers-jet-which-went-missing-over-afghanistan-2024-01-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jan 2024 09:50:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>载有6人的俄罗斯航班在阿富汗上空失踪；报告崩溃</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/report-plane-crash-northern-afghanistans-badakhshan-province-police-2024-01-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯航空当局表示，这架飞机是一架救护包机，乘坐法国制造的达索航空猎鹰10号喷气式飞机，从泰国芭堤雅乌塔保机场出发，途经印度和乌兹别克斯坦飞往莫斯科。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/report-plane-crash-northern-afghanistans-badakhshan-province-police-2024-01-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jan 2024 07:16:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾马科斯因使用直升机观看酷玩乐队演唱会而惹怒</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/philippines-marcos-draws-ire-helicopter-use-coldplay-concert-2024-01-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯因乘坐总统直升机前往首都马尼拉北部省份参加英国摇滚乐队酷玩乐队的音乐会而在社交媒体上遭到严厉批评。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/philippines-marcos-draws-ire-helicopter-use-coldplay-concert-2024-01-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jan 2024 02:26:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚在热浪中出汗，厄尔尼诺现象增加了丛林火灾风险</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-sweats-heatwave-lifting-bushfire-risk-amid-el-nino-2024-01-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周日，澳大利亚大片地区再次因不断扩大的热浪而变得闷热，国家天气预报员表示，由于该国正经历厄尔尼诺天气模式，在本已高风险的火灾季节，这增加了丛林火灾的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-sweats-heatwave-lifting-bushfire-risk-amid-el-nino-2024-01-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jan 2024 00:15:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝鲜表示普京愿意很快访问平壤</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/putin-showed-intention-visit-pyongyang-soon-north-korea-says-2024-01-20/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这将是这位俄罗斯领导人二十多年来首次访问朝鲜。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/putin-showed-intention-visit-pyongyang-soon-north-korea-says-2024-01-20/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 23:18:33 GMT</pubDate>
